general.desc: Zhe Kuang Heavy Industry Co Ltd is engaged in design, production and sales of mining machinery and equipment such as cone crusher and jaw crusher. It manufactures hydraulic system, transmission device, equipment complete machine and intelligent management system of complete equipment. The company's products include mobile crusher; crushing equipment, feeding & converying; and screening & washing.
